  "original_title": "IMF \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c \u0dc3\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0da0\u0dca\u0da1\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dae\u0d9a\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Negotiations with the IMF are successful",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Central Bank Governor Dr. Nandalal Weerasinghe says that Sri Lanka has made \"good progress\" in negotiations with the International Monetary Fund (IMF) to obtain an extended credit facility.",
        "\u201cI can state that we have made good progress in the discussions with the International Monetary Fund. Hopefully, we will be able to reach the first milestone, which is a staff-level agreement with the IMF,\u201d the central bank governor said. He said this at a press conference held in Colombo."
      ],
